data.description: Discover the perfect place to call home!  You will be immediately drenched in natural light and greeted by the Sandia Mountains with picturesque views out of the living, kitchen, and dining rooms. Located in North Albuquerque Acres, this .89 acre property offers a sprawling ranch style home that has beautiful and modern updates: kitchen cabinets, counters, appliances, light fixtures, paint, laundry room/pantry, expansive primary closet system, bathroom vanities and flooring in all of the bedrooms.  Huge new 1200sq ft RV/Boat Garage in the back, and oversized 3 car attached garage; storage and workspace is plentiful! Highly rated schools (Double Eagle, Desert Ridge and La Cueva), easy access to Paseo and I25 and close to police station, shopping and restaurants!
